  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" Hindi songs to sing can be subjective, as it often depends on personal preference, vocal range, and the occasion. However, here are some popular and beloved Hindi songs across various genres that are often enjoyed for singing:\n\n1. **Classic Bollywood Hits:**\n   - \"Lag Ja Gale\" from **Woh Kaun Thi** (1964)\n   - \"Tum Hi Ho\" from **Aashiqui 2** (2013)\n   - \"Kabhi Kabhi Mere Dil Mein\" from **Kabhi Kabhie** (1976)\n   - \"Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas\" from **Blackmail** (1973)\n   - \"Tere Bina Zindagi Se Koi Shikwa\" from **Aandhi** (1975)\n\n2. **Modern Bollywood Favorites:**\n   - \"Channa Mereya\" from **Ae Dil Hai Mushkil** (2016)\n   - \"Kal Ho Naa Ho\" from **Kal Ho Naa Ho** (2003)\n   - \"Tum Mile\" from **Tum Mile** (2009)\n   - \"Raabta\" from **Agent Vinod** (2012)\n   - \"Jeene Laga Hoon\" from **Ramaiya Vastavaiya** (2013)\n\n3. **Romantic Melodies:**\n   - \"Pehla Nasha\" from **Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar** (1992)\n   - \"Tujh Mein Rab Dikhta Hai\" from **Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi** (2008)\n   - \"Sun Saathiya\" from **ABCD 2** (2015)\n   - \"Dil Diyan Gallan\" from **Tiger Zinda Hai** (2017)\n   - \"Tum Jo Aaye\" from **Once Upon a Time in Mumbaai** (2010)\n\n4. **Upbeat and Energetic Songs:**\n   - \"Badtameez Dil\" from **Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani** (2013)\n   - \"Gallan Goodiyan\" from **Dil Dhadakne Do** (2015)\n   - \"Senorita\" from **Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara** (2011)\n   - \"Lungi Dance\" from **Chennai Express** (2013)\n   - \"Kar Gayi Chull\" from **Kapoor & Sons** (2016)\n\n5. **Soulful Tracks:**\n   - \"Agar Tum Saath Ho\" from **Tamasha** (2015)\n   - \"Ae Dil Hai Mushkil\" from **Ae Dil Hai Mushkil** (2016)\n   - \"Kun Faya Kun\" from **Rockstar** (2011)\n   - \"Zara Zara\" from **RHTDM** (2001)\n   - \"Phir Le Aaya Dil\" from **Barfi!** (2012)\n\nThese songs cover a range of emotions and styles, making them great choices for different moods and occasions. Whether you're singing for a performance, karaoke, or just for fun, these tracks are sure to resonate with audiences.",
